{"tid":2040021,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"邊個話馬車死鳩左？3男子認毆「劉馬車」判社服緩刑　劉困內地被通緝","createTime":"2020-05-28T10:14:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-30T21:32:54.000Z","uid":213877,"like":135,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":73,"replies":[{"pid":"58641ed76b6c5536283f540e645e9689faee1022","tid":2040021,"uid":213877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T10:14:04.000Z","msg":"3男子認毆「劉馬車」判社服緩刑 劉困內地被通緝<br />\n[/b]<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200528/bkn-20200528164316055-0528_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20200528%2Fbkn-20200528164316055-0528_00822_001.html&d=hmvw4%2FD%2BM9RG0cIfJpNLu7HKdwoo7KeUephkEgg9e70%3D&h=8963b96a\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200528/bkn-20200528164316055-0528_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200528/photo/bkn-20200528164316055-0528_00822_001_01p.jpg?20200528164320\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20200528%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200528164316055-0528_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20200528164320&h=b56cde90&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n控方確認劉駿軒於去年7月中在內地被拘留至今。<br />\n<br />\n自稱「劉馬車」的網絡紅人劉駿軒，去年中在街上疑因眼神問題，與3名廚房工人爭執。劉先出手襲擊對方其中1人，結果反遭圍毆。3名廚工兩星期前在屯門裁判法院承認襲擊致造成身體傷害罪，今天（28日）分別被判社會服務令及緩刑。至於劉則因在本案發生後於內地就其他事件被公安拘捕，現時仍未回港，故仍被通緝中。<br />\n<br />\n本案3名被告甘翊恒（29歲）、李啟華（43歲）及李斯維（20歲），均在天水圍屏欣商場翠河餐廳工作。案情透露，去年7月9日晚上10時許，3人在餐廳外抽煙，期間劉駿軒經過上址，4人因眼神問題起爭執。3名被告其後返回餐廳，但劉尾隨他們入餐廳，更先出手拳打第李斯維的胸部，3人隨即還手拳打腳踢劉，李斯維更拿櫈打劉的背部。<br />\n<br />\n其後3名被告的同事報警，最終4人一同被捕。因傷勢不重，3名被告拒絕求醫，而劉則自行到屯門醫院求診，證實其右膝擦損，咀唇擦損及紅腫，另外頭皮發紅。<br />\n<br />\n3名被告在本月14日認罪後，裁判官為他們索取社會服務令報告，押後至今日判刑。裁判官參考報告後，決定判甘翊恒與李啟華100小時社會服務令，李斯維就判監2星期緩刑12個月。<br />\n<br />\n至於劉的情況，控方就表示接收到情報，他在去年7月16日於內地被拘留至今。港方已向內地公安查問他在內地犯事之詳情，現仍等待答覆。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n天無眼，未死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92890f0abadc99c76a16e8fe50aae910f63c828c","tid":2040021,"uid":122134,"like":84,"dislike":3,"score":81,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T10:15:12.000Z","msg":"搵人去wiki個度改返佢<br />\n已返生"},{"pid":"aa6e1b9f2e1a6b7c592c81b609ae379a0cdfddc1","tid":2040021,"uid":213877,"like":11,"dislike":2,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"92890f0abadc99c76a16e8fe50aae910f63c828c","tid":2040021,"uid":122134,"like":84,"dislike":3,"score":81,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T10:15:12.000Z","msg":"搵人去wiki個度改返佢<br />\n已返生"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T10:15:58.000Z","msg":"天無眼，未死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2f8fdd75c2a531093efe327a1de1ccf94cbca5a","tid":2040021,"uid":255763,"like":28,"dislike":2,"score":26,"quote":{"pid":"92890f0abadc99c76a16e8fe50aae910f63c828c","tid":2040021,"uid":122134,"like":84,"dislike":3,"score":81,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T10:15:12.000Z","msg":"搵人去wiki個度改返佢<br />\n已返生"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T10:19:36.000Z","msg":"劉馬車(被復活)"},{"pid":"f338a19de1d102930395846727e64341d040606a","tid":2040021,"uid":35717,"like":25,"dislike":1,"score":24,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T10:21:56.000Z","msg":"比人拘留左差唔多成年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又衰咩<br />\n如果返到黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又比人拉， 好唔得閒"},{"pid":"388bde21b49a5899083029879af10eb63ac5288b","tid":2040021,"uid":24788,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T10:22:40.000Z","msg":"7月問到依家仲未覆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"969cb4ed879df7cf131828d5a16b3063b4f8d221","tid":2040021,"uid":61976,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T10:24:26.000Z","msg":"同事報警<br />\n好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa15e445ae21b28c10d0f2fe55fa1789aecfde17","tid":2040021,"uid":66331,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T10:25:25.000Z","msg